#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.210"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.210:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.210:0.2"
msgid "21. Sappurisavagga"
msgstr "21. A Good Person"

#. </p><h1>
#. VAR: dutiyapāpadhamma-kalyāṇadhammasuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.210:0.3"
msgid "210. Catutthapāpadhammasutta"
msgstr "210. Bad Character (4th)"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.210:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Pāpadhammañca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi, pāpadhammena pāpadhammatarañca;"
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach you bad character and worse character,"

msgctxt "an4.210:1.2"
msgid ""
"kalyāṇadhammañca, kalyāṇadhammena kalyāṇadhammatarañca. Taṃ suṇātha … pe …."
msgstr "good character and better character."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.210:2.1"
msgid "“Katamo ca, bhikkhave, pāpadhammo?"
msgstr "And who has bad character?"

msgctxt "an4.210:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco micchādiṭṭhiko hoti … pe … micchāñāṇī hoti, "
"micchāvimutti hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has wrong view, wrong thought, wrong speech, wrong action, "
"wrong livelihood, wrong effort, wrong mindfulness, wrong immersion, wrong "
"knowledge, and wrong freedom."

msgctxt "an4.210:2.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, pāpadhammo."
msgstr "This is called bad character."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.225"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.210:3.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, pāpadhammena pāpadhammataro?"
msgstr "And who has worse character?"

msgctxt "an4.210:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco attanā ca micchādiṭṭhiko hoti, parañca "
"micchādiṭṭhiyā samādapeti … pe … attanā ca micchāñāṇī hoti, parañca "
"micchāñāṇe samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has wrong view, wrong thought, wrong speech, wrong action, "
"wrong livelihood, wrong effort, wrong mindfulness, wrong immersion, wrong "
"knowledge, and wrong freedom. And they encourage others in these same "
"qualities."

msgctxt "an4.210:3.3"
msgid "attanā ca micchāvimutti hoti, parañca micchāvimuttiyā samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.210:3.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, pāpadhammena pāpadhammataro."
msgstr "This is called worse character."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.210:4.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, kalyāṇadhammo?"
msgstr "And who has good character?"

msgctxt "an4.210:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco sammādiṭṭhiko hoti … pe … sammāñāṇī hoti, "
"sammāvimutti hoti."
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has right view, right thought, right speech, right action, "
"right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, right immersion, right "
"knowledge, and right freedom."

msgctxt "an4.210:4.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kalyāṇadhammo."
msgstr "This is called good character."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.210:5.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, kalyāṇadhammena kalyāṇadhammataro?"
msgstr "And who has better character?"

msgctxt "an4.210:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco attanā ca sammādiṭṭhiko hoti, parañca sammādiṭṭhiyā "
"samādapeti … pe … attanā ca sammāñāṇī hoti, parañca sammāñāṇe samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s someone who has right view, right thought, right speech, right action, "
"right livelihood, right effort, right mindfulness, right immersion, right "
"knowledge, and right freedom. And they encourage others in these same "
"qualities."

msgctxt "an4.210:5.3"
msgid "attanā ca sammāvimutti hoti, parañca sammāvimuttiyā samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.210:5.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, kalyāṇadhammena kalyāṇadhammataro”ti."
msgstr "This is called better character.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.210:5.5"
msgid "Dasamaṃ."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.210:5.6"
msgid "Sappurisavaggo paṭhamo."
msgstr ""

#. </p><blockquote class="uddanagatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "an4.210:6.1"
msgid "Sikkhāpadañca assaddhaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.210:6.2"
msgid "Sattakammaṃ atho ca dasakammaṃ;"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.210:6.3"
msgid "Aṭṭhaṅgikañca dasamaggaṃ,"
msgstr ""

#. <br>
msgctxt "an4.210:6.4"
msgid "Dve pāpadhammā apare dveti."
msgstr ""
